app_name: Groups Control Groups Messenger Apps uchat secureapp
app_description: UChat is simple reliable and private so you can easily keep in touch with your friends and family. Your personal messages and calls to friends and family are end to end encrypted. No one outside of your chats not even UChat Team can read or listen to them. Simple and secure connections right away All you need is your phone number no user names or logins. You can quickly view your contacts who are on UChat and start messaging.
